name: RRR (Rise Roar Revolt)
description: A fearless warrior on a perilous mission comes face to face with a steely cop serving British forces in this epic saga set in pre-independent India.

name: K.G.F: Chapter 2
description: In the blood-soaked Kolar Gold Fields, Rocky's name strikes fear into his foes, while the government sees him as a threat to law and order. Rocky must battle threats from all sides for unchallenged supremacy.

name: Ponniyin Selvan: Part One
description: Vandiyathevan crosses the Chola land to deliver a message from the Crown Prince Aditha Karikalan, while Kundavai attempts to establish political peace as vassals and petty chieftains plot against the throne.

name: Brahmastra Part One: Shiva
description: A DJ with superpowers and his ladylove embark on a mission to protect the Brahmastra, a weapon of enormous energy, from dark forces closing in on them.

name: Vikram
description: A special investigator discovers a case of serial killings is not what it seems to be, and leading down this path is only going to end in a war between everyone involved.

name: Kantara
description: When greed paves the way for betrayal, scheming and murder, a young tribal reluctantly dons the traditions of his ancestors to seek justice.

name: Drishyam 2
description: A gripping tale of an investigation and a family which is threatened by it. Will Vijay Salgaonkar be able to protect his family this time?

name: The Kashmir Files
description: A heart-wrenching tale that captures the pain, suffering, and struggle of the Kashmiri Pandit community in 1990 and leads Krishna, a young college student, to set out on a quest to uncover the truth.

name: Bhool Bhulaiyaa 2
description: When strangers Reet and Ruhan cross paths, their journey leads to an abandoned mansion and a dreaded spirit that has been trapped for 18 years.

name: Beast
description: A jaded former intelligence agent is pulled back into action when an attack at a mall creates a tense hostage situation.

name: Gangubai Kathiawadi
description: Duped and sold to a brothel, a young woman fearlessly reclaims her power, using underworld connections to preside over the world she was once a pawn in.

name: Sarkaru Vaari Paata
description: After being conned by the woman he loves, a finance agent arrives in India from USA to retrieve his money from the woman's father who is a powerful MP and industrialist.

name: Valimai
description: Arjun, an IPS officer sets out for a mission on hunting down illegal bikers involving in theft and murder.

name: Bheemla Nayak
description: Things change when the egos of an upright police officer and a retired army havildar clash.

name: Radhe Shyam
description: Love blooms between a doctor with an uncertain future and a renowned palmist who thought he would never find love. His beliefs are challenged.

name: Jug Jugg Jeeyo
description: Two couples from different generations confront their issues after marriage.

name: Vikram Vedha
description: A tough police officer sets out to track down and kill an equally tough gangster.

name: Laal Singh Chaddha
description: The story of Laal Singh Chaddha, a simple man whose extraordinary journey will fill you with love, warmth and happiness.

name: Karthikeya 2
description: A sequel to Karthikeya (2014), which deals with the personal problems of Karthikeya and how his pursuit of the truth leads him to find out the power of Indian ancient system and Tatva of Lord Sri Krishna.

name: Thiruchitrambalam
description: Thiruchitrambalam lives with his father and grandfather. He blames the former for the loss of his mother and sister and is not on good terms with the latter. Meanwhile, his love life is not so successful.

name: Don
description: Follows the life of a youngster from college to his marriage.

name: Godfather
description: A political leader's death leads to a power struggle. Amid corruption, greed and deceit, an unlikely opponent steps up.

name: 777 Charlie
description: Dharma is stuck in a rut with his negative and lonely lifestyle and spends each day in the comfort of his loneliness. A pup named Charlie enters his life and gives him a new perspective towards it.

name: VR (Vikrant Rona)
description: Almost half a century ago, a remote village in the middle of a tropical rainforest starts witnessing a series of unexplainable events which they attribute to the supernatural.

name: Bhediya
description: Set in the forests of Arunachal, Bhediya is a story of Bhaskar, a man who gets bitten by a wolf, and begins to transform into the creature. As Bhaskar and his buddies try to find answers, a bunch of twists, turns, and laughs ensue.

name: Sita Ramam
description: An orphan soldier, Lieutenant Ram's life changes, after he gets a letter from a girl named Sita. He meets her and love blossoms between them. When he comes back to his camp in Kashmir,After he gets caught in jail, he sends a lette...

name: James
description: James also called Santhosh Kumar, who works as a manager in a security company and finds himself up against the big bad guys.

name: Samrat Prithviraj
description: A magnum opus recounting the glorious tale of one of India's bravest emperors- Samrat Prithviraj Chauhan. Inspired from the epic poem Prithviraj Raaso and other folklores.

name: F3: Fun and Frustration
description: Venky and Varun, who try to come up from financial problems. But what will happen when they meet Pragathi Family who are greedy for money?

name: Bheeshmaparvam
description: Michael helms his ancestral family in Kochi, inspiring fear and respect through his past. When a few younger members of the household find his power over their lives too aggravating, they join hands with foes to clamp down on him.

name: Sardar
description: A spy, who is estranged from his family due to a mission, suddenly meets his police officer son.

name: Love Today
description: Two young lovers, who are made to exchange their phones for a day and what happens due to that.

name: Dhamaka
description: Swamy and Anand who look exactly the same, come from different backgrounds. Under dicey circumstances Pranavi, a young and pretty girl falls in love with both of them. How will Swamy and Anand solve their problems?

name: Bachchhan Paandey
description: When a struggling filmmaker and actor set out to make a biography on one of the most dreaded gangsters, they have little idea about just how crazy and dangerous it's going to be.

name: Acharya
description: Touted to be a socio-political actioner, the plot revolves around a middle-aged Naxalite-turned-social reformer who launches a fight against the Endowments Department over misappropriation of temple funds and donations.

name: Etharkkum Thunindhavan
description: A lawyer turns judge jury and executioner and goes after a gang, led by a minister's son, that threatens women with videos of them.

name: Raksha Bandhan
description: Lala Kedarnath promises his dying mother to marry his 4 sisters well. Owner of family chat shop, he has trouble finding suitors. His sisters take priority over childhood romance with Sapna.

name: Bimbisara
description: The protagonist time travels from his kingdom to the present world. How and why does he do it?

name: Viruman
description: An intrepid and good-hearted son fights to make his arrogant father pay the price for his sins, which includes his mother's death, and save his brothers from the man's grip.

name: Bangarraju
description: Bangarraju and Satyabhama come down to settle the life of their grandson Chinna Bangarraju and to save the treasure of temple.

name: Shamshera
description: Shamshera (Ranbir Kapoor), leader of an imprisoned tribe, failed to escape for their freedom. Years later his son Balli realizes his father's legacy.

name: Cirkus
description: Two sets of identical twins are accidentally separated at birth. Several years later, when they are coincidentally in the same town, there is a lot of confusion and misunderstanding when people mistake them for each other.

name: Ek Villain Returns
description: The story of two men in one sided love. The paths they choose to fulfill their love stories decide who the Hero is and who is the Villain.

name: Cobra
description: A mathematician genius, Mathi, has another identity, Cobra, who commits intelligent crimes using maths.

name: Major
description: Based on the life of Major Sandeep Unnikrishnan, who was martyred in action during the November 2008 Mumbai attacks.

name: Liger
description: A story about martial arts, dreams and star crossed lovers. Liger is an MMA fighter who trains hard and rises up the ranks with one goal in mind, to fight like his idol, world renowned MMA fighter Mark Anderson and get noticed by ...

name: Vendhu Thanindhathu Kaadu
description: Muthu, a low caste youngster, goes to the streets of Mumbai for a living. His quest takes him to a series of unexpected events, where he gets involved in the underground activities of Mumbai's Tamil gangsters. Will he get to the top?

name: Hridayam
description: The emotional journey of Arun, his carefree bachelor days in engineering college, and how he matures through various phases of life.

name: Kaathu Vaakula Rendu Kaadhal
description: It follows the romance of Rambo with Kanmani and Khatija.

name: Malikappuram
description: An intense desire of Kallu an 8 year old girl from Panchalimedu village to visit Sabarimala.

name: Runway 34
description: Inspired by true incidents, "Runway 34" revolves around Captain Vikrant Khanna played by Ajay Devgn, a flying prodigy, whose flight takes a mysterious course after take-off from an international destination.

name: Thank God
description: An egoistic real estate broker in huge debts, meets with an accident.God appears in front of him and informs him that he will have to play a "GAME OF LIFE". If he win, he will be sent back to earth and if not, he will be sent to h...

name: Jana Gana Mana
description: As a college professor's brutal murder sparks student unrest, a cop launches an investigation while a lawyer seeks justice in the the courtroom.

name: Uunchai
description: Three friends take a trek to the Everest Base Camp. A simple trek turns out to be a personal, emotional and spiritual journey as they battle their physical limitations and discover the true meaning of freedom.

name: Rocketry: The Nambi Effect
description: The story of Indian Space Research Organization scientist Nambi Narayanan, who was framed for being a spy and arrested in 1994.

name: Kaduva
description: The film is set in the late 90s revolving around the life of a young high range rubber planter from Mundakayam and his rivalry with a high ranking officer in the Kerala Police.

name: Doctor G
description: Uday Gupta finds himself as the lone male resident in the Gynaecology department. His reluctance leads to chaos, confusion, comedy and eventually, great camaraderie with his fellow classmates.

name: Jaya Jaya Jaya Jaya Hey
description: Jaya, gets married. Her intention is to complete her education, but her partner mockingly asks her to try for Public Service Commission exams. Jaya tries to find the right balance managing her in-laws as she strives for her goal.

name: HIT: The 2nd Case
description: Krishna Dev aka KD, a laid back cop, works in AP HIT, has to take up a gruesome murder case. As KD unravels the layers of the crime, the stakes rise unbelievably high and the threat comes unusually close.

name: Prince
description: A teacher falls in love with a young British woman who works as an English teacher at the same school. He tries to woo her, leads conflicts that come crashing on them as they face the biggest battle of their lives - to get married.

name: Thallumaala
description: Follows a youngster ready to get married, but funny events happen and changes his plans.

name: Rorschach
description: The Movie is about Luke Anthony who has a mysterious past and is out on a mission to seek revenge from someone who has destroyed him deeply

name: Ante Sundharaniki
description: A Hindu Brahmin falls for a Christian girl and they both lie to their parents, only for their lies to be revealed.

name: Naane Varuvean
description: Prabhu an average suburban man for whom his family is everything. His life is turned upside down when his daughter Satya is possessed by the ghost of a little boy.

name: The Warriorr
description: When Satya raises his voice against Guru, the latter revolts and bashes the former to hell. Satya makes a comeback as a cop to take revenge on Guru and put an end to his crime in Kurnool city.

name: CBI 5
description: A series of murders is happening in the city. With the police failing to solve the case, a team of CBI Officers under CBI officer Sethurama Iyer take up the investigation to resolve the mystery.

name: Heropanti 2
description: Babloo Ranawat, a genius hacker, is tasked with tracking down Laila, the mastermind behind the world's largest cyber-crime yet to occur. Will Babloo be able to stop him?

name: Nna Thaan Case Kodu
description: A reformed thief's fight for justice when an innocent act to defend himself places him in loggerheads with the high and mighty of society.

name: Yashoda
description: In a highly regimented facility housing surrogate mothers, a pregnant woman discovers that things are not as they seem.

name: DJ Tillu
description: A lazy young man spends his time chasing girls, until an incident changes his life forever.

name: Paappan
description: A gripping crime investigation journey of Kerala Police confronted by an ex-cop Abraham Mathew Mathan aka Paappan. As he dives deeper into the case, destiny has an emotional tryst in store for him.

name: Badhaai Do
description: Shardul Thakur Flaglot and Suman Singh enter into a marriage of convenience but chaos ensues when her unhinged girlfriend comes to stay with them.

name: Jersey
description: A cricketer who quits cricket decides to revive his career at the age of 36 for his sons dream and prove his ability.

name: Khiladi
description: A murder suspect escapes police custody due to criminologist Priya's misjudgment of her case for the thesis. Priya along with Arjun solves the mystery around the murder and money laundering which lead to the murder.

name: Attack
description: Witness the rise of an army soldier as he realizes his destiny and comes to terms to becoming India's first super soldier created to combat terrorists as he fights his inner demons and outer enemies.With lots of action

name: Kanam
description: To set their present right, Aadhi and his friends decide to take a ride with time to set their past right through a scientist. But time had other plans for them.

name: Jhund
description: Based on the life of Vijay Barse, a retired sports teacher who founded an NGO called Slum Soccer. He managed to rehabilitate street kids by keeping them off drugs and crime by turning them into soccer players and building a whole ...

name: 18 Pages
description: Nandini, a young woman who loves living an orthodox life without being bound to technology uses a diary to keep track of her life. But, when her diary is lost, Sidhu finds it. Drawn to the person he reads about, he sets out to fin...

name: Aaraattu
description: Neyyattinkara Gopan, an influential goon is stepping in to help Edathala Mathai do an illegal conversion of an 18-acre paddy field. But is he really who he says he is?

name: Yaanai
description: PRV's family who lives with his two wives and children in Ramnad district.. Also, there is a family who is convinced that PRV's family only caused the death of his brother. The movie narrates many incidents that happen in the two ...

name: Chup
description: A lonesome florist with a new-found love interest and a psychopath killer who targets film critics in Mumbai. Are the two related? Inspector Arvind Mathur and Dr. Zenobia are about to find out.
